Installation:

	git clone git://github.com/phester571/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
	ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Load submodules:
	cd ~/.vim
	git submodule init
	git submodule update

Update all submodules:
	cd ~/.vim
	git submodule foreach git pull origin master
